        "timestamp": "2018-09-18 14:19:42.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nJessica, if you're able to weigh in, let me know.  A number of ways we could proceed:\n1. If you could isolate this change into an independent PR, we can push it in.\n2. We can push in the parent PR as well (my only concern was that your changes will get clobbered until we can also line up the project.clj)\n3. I can recreate the isolated change to test the build pipeline in a separate PR and we'll merge that.  Will re-use the Issue ID so you can track it.\n\nFor everyone else - I propose to go with Option #3 if we don't hear back from Jess by about early-afternoon (mid-morning, pacific) - I usually don't hear from her until late evening (a testament to both her dedication as well as her likely crushing workload), and I think we're all keen to test her change.",
